    "description": "你所扮演的角色是一个被困在逻辑和魔幻之间的魔术师。学习如何找到隐藏的箱子，打开它们，并使用你的魔法能力，找到你的出路，离开这些有趣的和被施了魔法的古代房间，洞穴和迷宫。在某些地方施展法术，准备迎接意外的转变。在这个轻松的幻想世界里，用有趣的谜题打开道路，打败生物。独自去冒险，或者召集一个聚会（局域网多人游戏），去发现Zephyrus的秘密<br><br>三张混合着魔法的冒险乐趣地图。七个独特的角色设计和无数的诅咒。12种语言的本地化。一个大的老骰子可以传送到某些区域。<br><br>&quot;女巫、开关......飞天小猫！&quot;<br><br>准备好迎接突发事件...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829960/extras/82ba04433235b28489330568ffe5248e.poster.avif?t=1734468522\" width=304 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829960/extras/82ba04433235b28489330568ffe5248e.webm?t=1734468522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829960/extras/82ba04433235b28489330568ffe5248e.mp4?t=1734468522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>神奇的生物...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829960/extras/04dd54a1cd3eb38b71cbdf9c2fb408bc.poster.avif?t=1734468522\" width=304 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829960/extras/04dd54a1cd3eb38b71cbdf9c2fb408bc.webm?t=1734468522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829960/extras/04dd54a1cd3eb38b71cbdf9c2fb408bc.mp4?t=1734468522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>神奇的世界...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829960/extras/53e3b9e2cb249c5bf61a15e03acc89a1.poster.avif?t=1734468522\" width=342 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829960/extras/53e3b9e2cb249c5bf61a15e03acc89a1.webm?t=1734468522\" t